WEBVTT


00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.755
Let me be clear about when it comes to,

00:00:01.756 --> 00:00:03.611
the most dangerous party in this country

00:00:03.612 --> 00:00:04.411
this is the AfD.

00:00:04.617 --> 00:00:06.315
Now I have to see what they demanded.

00:00:06.316 --> 00:00:07.737
They want us to get out of the EU.

00:00:07.983 --> 00:00:10.562
That would be 1 economic fiasco for Germany,

00:00:10.563 --> 00:00:11.549
out From NATO,

00:00:11.583 --> 00:00:13.640
we would surrender Putin,

00:00:13.641 --> 00:00:14.723
No business tax

00:00:14.724 --> 00:00:16.306
more main source of revenue for municipalities,

00:00:16.307 --> 00:00:17.461
so no outdoor pools,

00:00:17.462 --> 00:00:18.341
no women's shelters,

00:00:18.342 --> 00:00:19.277
No daycare centers

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:21.033
for the little people or the little people.

00:00:21.034 --> 00:00:22.031
Don't do anything on the right,

00:00:22.032 --> 00:00:23.326
Retirement ages are to be high.

00:00:23.454 --> 00:00:24.570
Must say quite clearly,

00:00:24.571 --> 00:00:26.626
this party makes politics

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.522
against the majority of people in the country,

00:00:28.523 --> 00:00:29.481
against their worries,

00:00:29.482 --> 00:00:31.211
because they benefit from these concerns.

00:00:31.260 --> 00:00:34.380
And the AfD is at its core an antisocial party,

00:00:34.381 --> 00:00:36.161
that wants to destabilize this country.
